[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0752","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0502","title":"Unix SSH 默认空密码远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统存在默认账户密码为空、未设置或使用弱口令的安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过 SSH 服务识别此类弱口令账户，利用 Metasploit 框架等自动化工具进行登录尝试，成功后可获取目标系统的未授权 shell 访问权限，进而执行任意命令或实施横向移动。该漏洞广泛影响各类 Unix/Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。加固措施包括删除或禁用默认账户、强制设置强密码策略。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0502"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.960","remediation":"立即为所有 Unix 系统账户设置强密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符），禁用空口令账户（`passwd -l` 锁定无密码账户），并配置 `/etc/shadow` 确保口令哈希非空。在 SSH 配置文件 `/etc/ssh/sshd_config` 中设置 `PermitEmptyPasswords no` 并重启 sshd 服务。建议安装并运行 `john` 或 `hydra` 扫描弱口令账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0502","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41694"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0545","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0330","title":"Linux bdash 游戏缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux bdash 游戏程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向游戏程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获取 root 权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 bdash 游戏的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击前提是攻击者拥有系统的本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0330"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.070","remediation":"立即移除 bdash 游戏的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/games/bdash），或直接卸载 bsdgames 软件包以彻底消除提权风险。如确需保留该游戏，应升级至已修复缓冲区边界检查的修补版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319119&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0532","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0320","title":"Sun SunOS rpc.cmsd 任意文件覆盖提权漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统的 rpc.cmsd（日历管理服务守护进程）存在任意文件覆写漏洞。rpc.cmsd 以 root 权限运行，由于对用户提交的 RPC 参数缺乏充分的路径验证，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的日历管理服务发送特制 RPC 请求，覆写任意系统文件，从而获取 root 访问权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3 至 5.5.1（Solaris 2.3 至 2.5.1）版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0320"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.750","remediation":"针对 SunOS/Solaris 2.x 系统，安装 Sun Security Bulletin #166 提供的对应版本补丁：Solaris 2.3 安装 101318 补丁、Solaris 2.4 安装 101945 补丁、Solaris 2.5 安装 103093 补丁、Solaris 2.5.1 安装 103094 补丁。如业务不需要日历管理服务，可停止 rpc.cmsd 守护进程（/etc/init.d/calendar stop）并注释 rpc 绑定条目作为临时缓解。对于仍在运行的遗留系统，建议迁移至 Oracle Solaris 11 及以上受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/166"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0451","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0266","title":"Info2www CGI 输入处理远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Info2www 是一个用于将 GNU Info 文档转换为 HTML 格式的 CGI 脚本程序。该脚本对用户输入的参数缺乏充分的过滤与验证，远程攻击者可通过向 info2www CGI 脚本发送特制请求，利用输入处理缺陷实现任意文件读取或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Info2www 1.0 及 1.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0266"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.100","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器移除 info2www CGI 脚本目录（通常位于 /cgi-bin/info2www），或删除 info2www 文件。如仍需此类功能，改用维护中的替代方案（如 Pinfo）。通过 Web 服务器配置限制 CGI 目录执行权限，确保仅授权用户可执行，并在 WAF 层过滤包含特殊字符（如 |、;、`、$()）的 CGI 请求参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1995","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20430","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0266","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0484","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0290","title":"Qbik WinGate Telnet Proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate Telnet 代理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者通过向目标系统的 Telnet 代理端口发起大量本地主机连接请求，可耗尽代理服务资源导致服务崩溃，无法正常处理后续合法连接。该漏洞影响 Qbik WinGate 的 Telnet 代理模块，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，风险等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0290"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.970","remediation":"建议升级 WinGate 至 4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续迭代中修复。如无法升级，可在 WinGate 网关属性中禁用 telnet 代理服务（取消 Telnet Proxy 复选框），或在防火墙上限制对 telnet 代理端口（默认 23）的入站连接数量，仅允许可信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wingate_denial.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0537","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0537.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0323","title":"FreeBSD mmap 函数访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统内核中的 mmap 内存映射函数存在文件属性绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过调用 mmap 系统接口，绕过文件系统的保护机制，修改被设置为仅追加（append-only）或不可变（immutable）属性的文件内容。攻击者需要具备目标系统的本地账户权限，通过编写恶意程序调用 mmap 对受保护文件进行写入操作，可导致篡改系统关键配置文件、日志文件或安全策略，破坏系统完整性。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0323"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.107","remediation":"建议升级至 NetBSD 1.4+ 或 FreeBSD 3.0+ 版本，其中已修复 mmap(2) 系统调用对不可变/仅追加文件的权限检查缺陷。对于 NetBSD 1.3/1.3.1，可应用的补丁（来自 ftp://ftp.NetBSD.ORG/pub/NetBSD/misc/security/patches/19980509-mmap）。如无法升级临时缓解措施，可将系统 securelevel 提升至 1 以上并避免在多进程间对设定了 append-only/immutable 标志的文件使用共享可写 mmap。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82264/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c2ea8a31-4149-4cb6-8c91-11842551ba1b.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0537.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0411","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0225","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SMB 登录请求长度错误拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 SMB 登录验证服务在处理畸形登录请求时存在逻辑缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送实际数据大小与指定大小不符的特制 SMB 登录请求包，导致目标系统 LSASS 进程崩溃或系统蓝屏，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本，攻击条件简单，无需用户交互。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0225"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.050","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 SMB 登录请求中数据大小校验缺失导致的拒绝服务漏洞。同时建议在网络防火墙层面阻断来自不可信网络的 SMB 端口（TCP 139/445）入站流量。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持超过 20 年，长期缓解措施应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=180963","http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/25_windows_nt_dos_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0225","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/b253eed42806cfea7592c1858184a214ab406ebe/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000260.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0443","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0258","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 IP Fragmentation 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 4.0 的 IP 碎片重组模块存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形 IP 分片数据包（Bonk 变种），利用 UDP 协议的分片偏移量计算错误，导致目标系统内核崩溃或蓝屏死机，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0258"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.117","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统，已不受此漏洞影响。若因特殊原因仍运行 Windows 95/NT 4.0，安装 Microsoft 1999 年安全更新 MS99-017（KB191725）可修复 IP 分段重组校验逻辑。临时缓解措施：在路由器/防火墙上阻断进入内网的畸形 IP 分片包，或限制入站 ICMP 流量降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88901842000424&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0258","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0258.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bonk.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0012","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 等多款 Web 服务器文件访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"微软 Windows 平台上的 IIS、FrontPage 及 Personal Web Server 等 Web 服务器存在访问控制绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含超长文件名的特制请求，绕过服务器的文件访问限制机制，读取本应受限的系统文件或敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0、Windows 2000 等系统版本中运行的 IIS 3.0/4.0、Microsoft FrontPage 97/98 及 Personal Web Server 等产品，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.0，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0012"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.700","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows 2000 及以上操作系统并部署 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，彻底消除此漏洞。若无法升级，可安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-009 提供的修补程序；另在 IIS 管理器中禁用 8.3 短文件名生成，并使用 URLScan 工具过滤包含连续点号、超长文件名段的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0733","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0486","title":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 超链接远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标用户发送特制的恶意超链接，当接收方客户端解析或渲染该链接时触发异常，导致应用程序崩溃。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需认证即可实施，影响使用 AIM 3.5 版本的用户系统稳定性，属于中等危害级别的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0486"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.007","remediation":"建议立即升级至 AOL Instant Messenger 4.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超链接处理逻辑缺陷。由于 AOL 已于 2017 年 12 月 15 日停止 AIM 所有服务且软件不再受支持，当前应从所有设备卸载 AIM，迁移至仍受支持的即时通讯工具，并在防火墙及邮件网关中拦截相关协议的连接请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0486"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0510","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0305","title":"OpenBSD FreeBSD sysctl 源路由 TCP 连接欺骗漏洞","description":"BSD 系统（包括 OpenBSD 2.2 及更早版本、FreeBSD 2.2.5 及更早版本）的 sysctl 设施在设置 dosourceroute 或 forwarding 变量后，未能正确限制源路由数据包的处理，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷伪造 TCP 连接，绕过访问控制机制实施中间人攻击或会话劫持。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 和 FreeBSD 的早期版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0305"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.863","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.5 以上版本、OpenBSD 至 2.2 以上版本，或在系统配置中设置 sysctl 变量 net.inet.ip.doSourceroute=0 并禁用 IP 转发（sysctl net.inet.ip.forwarding=0），同时在边界防火墙上过滤源路由选项的数据包作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/advisories/sourceroute.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/11502","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/736"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0505","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0304","title":"BSD mmap 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 mmap 函数存在权限检查缺陷，属于 kmem 组的本地攻击者可通过操作设备文件实现对内核内存的未授权读写访问，进而提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响多种 BSD 衍生操作系统，攻击者需先获得本地低权限账户并属于 kmem 组方可利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0304"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.750","remediation":"建议立即升级至 FreeBSD 3.0 及以上已修复版本，或应用对应 BSD 厂商的安全补丁。严格限制 kmem 组成员仅限 root 用户，将 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 权限设为 600（仅 root 可读写）。可通过 sysctl -w security.bsd.mmap_of_physmem=0 禁止物理内存映射，并配置内核参数 kern.randompid=1 增强 ASLR 缓解效果。移除不必要的 kmem 组用户，避免被用于内核内存访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0304"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0441","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0256","title":"War-FTPD 1.65 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"War-FTPD 1.65 在处理用户登录时的密码字段存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的密码字符串触发基于栈的缓冲区溢出，导致服务器进程崩溃或在目标系统上执行任意代码。Metasploit 框架已集成该漏洞的利用模块，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0256"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.867","remediation":"升级 War-FTPD 至 1.82.00 RC 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Username/Password 栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。如该软件已停止维护，建议迁移至主动维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd、ProFTPD），并在防火墙限制对 FTP 服务的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/875","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16706","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0256","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/DDI_warftpd_user_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0087","title":"IBM AIX Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 Telnet 协议数据包，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致系统完全冻结，合法用户无法登录或访问服务器资源。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本，攻击门槛低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，IBM 已在后续维护版本中修复此问题。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并使用 refresh -s inetd 生效，改用 SSH 替代 telnet 服务，同时在防火墙上限制对 23/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0087","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0087","http://www.osvdb.org/7992"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0491","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0296","title":"Solaris volrmmount 程序任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统的 volrmmount 程序存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可以读取系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，需要本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0296"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1998-02-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Oracle Sun Security Bulletin 162 提供的补丁程序，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本。对于已停止支持的 Solaris 版本，建议迁移到受支持的 Solaris 11 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T16:49:07.408471690+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/162","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0296"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0491.toml"}]